OL,3,CThe roads going back to 30mph in
OL,4,CCardiff
OL,6,FCardiff Council has announced four
OL,7,Froads will be reverting back from
OL,8,F20mph to 30mph
OL,10,FIt follows the Welsh Government's
OL,11,Fguidance allowing councils to run
OL,12,Ftheir own reviews of 20mph roads and
OL,13,Fif there is justification to remain at
OL,14,F30mph.
OL,16,FThe roads set to change back are:
OL,18,FThere is no exact date for when the
OL,19,Froad signs will change, as it first
OL,20,Fneeds to go through a Traffic
OL,21,FRegulation Process.
