OL,6,FCllr Dan De'Ath, Cabinet Member for
OL,7,FStrategic Planning, Transport and
OL,8,FClimate Change said:
OL,10,F"Cardiff Council fully supports the
OL,11,FWelsh Government's 20mph policy and
OL,12,Fhas been using 20mph speed limits in
OL,13,Fthe city as far back as 2014.
