OL,3,CThe roads going back to 30mph in
OL,4,CCardiff
OL,6,FFollowing the review and 'listening
OL,7,Fexercise' with the public, the
OL,8,Funderlying principles remain
OL,9,Funchanged, a 20mph speed limit should
OL,10,Fremain in place in areas where
OL,11,Fpedestrians and cyclists frequently
OL,12,Fmix with motor vehicles unless strong
OL,13,Fevidence supports that higher speeds
OL,14,Fare safe.
OL,16,F"From the feedback received from the
OL,17,Fpublic and stakeholders, 192 roads in
OL,18,FCardiff were re-assessed using the
OL,19,Frevised Welsh Government guidance and
OL,20,Fassessment tools.
