OL,3,CThe roads going back to 30mph in
OL,4,CCardiff
OL,6,F"Following a thorough review,
OL,7,Fjustification was found to revert four
OL,8,Froads back to 30mph.
OL,10,FAll four roads are main routes into
OL,11,Fand out of the city. It makes sense to
OL,12,Frevert these back to 30mph to reduce
OL,13,Fcongestion and ensure consistency with
OL,14,Fadjoining roads and ongoing routes."
